        </div>

        <br>

        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <a href="{{ path('contact') }}" class="btn btn-success btn-lg m-auto">
                Hire us to make your Project Awesome
            </a>
        </div>

        {% include "_snippets/homepage_separator.twig" %}

        <h2>
            What Companies <span class="text-rector-blue">Love&nbsp;about&nbsp;Rector</span>?
        </h2>

        <blockquote class="blockquote clearfix">
            <img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/77585053/110624233-37728500-819e-11eb-9efb-269e161c2ad4.jpeg" class="rounded-circle img-face-smaller-left shadow me-5" alt="">

            <p>
                "Thanks to Rector, we were able to quite simply refactor the core of our API, which <strong>saved a lot of work</strong> that our developers would otherwise have to do manually."
            </p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer mt-2">
